ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5884d7a9f36f342cb2cfd962c5d482b4878d8e70","tid":462582,"uid":36263,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日覺得做守門好on9<br />\n企成場，真係發揮作用都唔知有冇十分鐘<br />\n<br />\n根本冇享受到踢波既樂趣</blockquote><br />\n你以為啦<br />\n打龍比場上任何一位球員都要專注同集中<br />\n因為一個決定就可以影響球隊士氣"},{"pid":"2b095a5b0f427e91192f7251903f844699203c95","tid":462582,"uid":123251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"守龍門係場上最後一個，睇到哂所有野，可以提出改善建議。當你救到波飛撲落地又或者擋到人地單刀係好有滿足感！"},{"pid":"f3c33650fcd0515906cd53243947b43d1d4ab129","tid":462582,"uid":9945,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"街場冇氣果陣最鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16111652ed95dcfae863ca87b96eb9f653b32799","tid":462582,"uid":53180,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"由細到大都守龍，但年紀大左(2x)淨係踢仿草同真草，<br />\n以前石地照飛撲，但撲得多有時飛完落地捨唔切力落地好撚傷。<br />\n利申:拎過業餘7人聯賽季軍"},{"pid":"13ce777ae03bfbd817e3c1151c44193abbc569aa","tid":462582,"uid":93200,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"屌做親龍 一比人入波就係龍既責任 之前我救左五六次先一入球就比人屌到屎忽開花 做龍狗也不屌 <br />\n救唔到波乜9責任都係龍既問題 係咁話點解唔咁咁咁 有次頂唔住話你咁勁你守 點知條友一守龍 比人起腳一次入一粒 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"605b75886bab065595e7117fc369f9231810248a","tid":462582,"uid":44171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"做籠救波時, 真係會感受到人肉慢鏡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e94188ca06151eebd7915e6dbe10a21bcbae00","tid":462582,"uid":55830,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做籠救波時, 真係會感受到人肉慢鏡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時睇野真係愈黎化慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f34dca65b85d7a0152c7264ddc2c25b002f2bfa","tid":462582,"uid":77484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:12:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a8192b26c5e9410a9c0a7b4e7d16a6bb8c0e260","tid":462582,"uid":34771,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:14:27.000Z","msg":"對面花咁多心力組織<br />\n一手破壞人地大事 感覺好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a01771f51dc46476d04de18d979b545da874cb","tid":462582,"uid":35730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"打後表示成日俾龍屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665528eb97499614d142adc01e262518a79cffea","tid":462582,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:42:41.000Z","msg":"做籠都好撚忙, 要提場, 唔係只望住個波, 叫人包抄, 叫MARK人, 次次叫到聲都沙, 真係睇住個波就死得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d39fa71fd9fc00640fd6b7e0679a1270e04854","tid":462582,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日覺得做守門好on9<br />\n企成場，真係發揮作用都唔知有冇十分鐘<br />\n<br />\n根本冇享受到踢波既樂趣</blockquote><br />\n你都on9,梗有人鍾意被人射"},{"pid":"79cb5d4b7d50a294a1c38c27594d602fc9ce3d88","tid":462582,"uid":71694,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"通常柒頭毒撚先俾人點去守龍，自問令仔風趣踢開前鋒😌"},{"pid":"bb1586203505a0cd56c36a8f71d0db328e43b819","tid":462582,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成也龍門；敗也龍門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n也門成龍；龍門也成</blockquote><br />\n龍成門也；門城龍也</blockquote><br />\n成龍龍門；龍門成龍"},{"pid":"7c34c1ce0d6fca8f3afba64b4be72e8dbf760a1c","tid":462582,"uid":140317,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"on9毒撚點打龍呀<br />\n