打最後果個做提場睇住條防線好過"},{"pid":"14d5568755faa8239175942fd94368d690ef49a8","tid":462582,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:35:06.000Z","msg":"唔洗跑，幾好丫"},{"pid":"8e39e1df0d3e869df90adfe7e0b6e17ad751bd5a","tid":462582,"uid":35730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申都係鐘意打龍<br />\n好好彩平時踢開班隊友好少會屌龍<br />\n有時係反而我覺得自己犯咗錯但都冇屌<br />\n(心入面個句唔知啦 但起碼冇當面屌你算係咁)</blockquote><br />\n因為隊友都知有d波真係無得救，救到只係bonus，反而打後發夢就真係會俾人屌"},{"pid":"dedbd4a4888a60920e3528a8611c377678b1817f","tid":462582,"uid":16283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日覺得做守門好on9<br />\n企成場，真係發揮作用都唔知有冇十分鐘<br />\n<br />\n根本冇享受到踢波既樂趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁大把球員成場都無作用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c0ffd8e3e6405071c36965b5f04feb02850ae2","tid":462582,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"以前都有兩個中學同學自願打龍<br />\n兩個都係肥仔<br />\n但佢地d救龍好犀利<br />\n<br />\n問佢地原因係話唔想跑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8fcac81eb6f7c7d8e689f6625395c7d4bea088","tid":462582,"uid":92072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"我淨係知落街場通常會叫啲肥仔守龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ade021c3130eb094865eab5e8c47f03fb027880","tid":462582,"uid":138953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我 但已經唔可以再守了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nching 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e549afdb96fd182d05521928fee813a51e29c690","tid":462582,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:44:31.000Z","msg":"個個星期三朝早都同班呀叔踢波<br />\n最撚候生已經係我<br />\n最快無氣要爭做龍又係我<br />\n<br />\n利申：26歲<img src=\