i\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e0560315730302f5068e685fb14c146db05579","tid":462582,"uid":86051,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:46:48.000Z","msg":"真係打龍有幾可俾人屌呀<br />\n龍門已經少<br />\n好既龍仲少<br />\n屌撚走左就自己受返<br />\n通常都係龍門屌人多<br />\n後衛俾人屌到開花"},{"pid":"3476a41b3b440cf7c62601a4c9d79f1735539ca4","tid":462582,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:49:55.000Z","msg":"好懷念中學踢街場既回憶"},{"pid":"bf1f18fd01b6795ce9fe2c163134d7dd283f9b66","tid":462582,"uid":79987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"曾經好中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d526e9b1466e5e9f10d30cc9b75a6db0cf15b7b5","tid":462582,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係打龍有幾可俾人屌呀<br />\n龍門已經少<br />\n好既龍仲少<br />\n屌撚走左就自己受返<br />\n通常都係龍門屌人多<br />\n後衛俾人屌到開花</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n做後既一有失誤好易俾人屌"},{"pid":"35f4f9998db28036961fcf585b3d066e1d7aef78","tid":462582,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n屌根本講緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：毒撚門將</blockquote><br />\n龍門唔嗌點做龍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過有時d龍門9嗌搞亂自己隊個後防又係好燥</blockquote><br />\n龍門嗌既理應係大晒<br />\n不過如果唔識嗌又鳩嗌咁真係大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好既龍嗌係真係可以幫到防守球員補到位，但鳩嗌果d真係我寧願打最後果個做提場睇住條防線好過</blockquote><br />\n一有角球佈防<br />\n大大聲:前柱一隻後柱兩個<br />\n睇埋禁區頂兩件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後飛身出去,大叫:我既<br />\n一個手搥打走個波<br />\n個種成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過一遇見近距離怒射就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n守角球試過俾自己龍出迎掃低"},{"pid":"1006ba5a05fc49f538c2adc2bedbb7899b65366a","tid":462582,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"點會冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01001001bee622dcd649f2668b466a6b51718a2e","tid":462582,"uid":73422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大都守龍，但年紀大左(2x)淨係踢仿草同真草，<br />\n以前石地照飛撲，但撲得多有時飛完落地捨唔切力落地好撚傷。<br />\n利申:拎過業餘7人聯賽季軍</blockquote><br />\n諗返以前我都石地照撲 好撚爽 但重傷過之後都冇再打過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b462655ef600540b83dc85a4525e4def208066","tid":462582,"uid":15013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"以前中學打手球係打龍<br />\n當大家都覺得輸硬嘅波 你一下撲救守住對面<br />\n果種霸氣同型 真係冇乜野代替到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe279e73d9adc6aedee05f3d3f243370d1cd8d2","tid":462582,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"次次自願做，因為唔夠氣跑成場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多都係打左翼，但半場就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c43878edb48a36bcf25ab1fb8adf6d7fbdf39e","tid":462582,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"龍門嗌後衛煩啲，定係後衛亂嗌keeper煩啲"},{"pid":"75434e8e55c6a9063e9c62e4384aa626165045db","tid":462582,"uid":10968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"入波會入到悶<br />\n但撲唔到波一粒都嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdc71748e7b79b43536ce8bb4c416c3ba5d8650","tid":462582,"uid":79658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍門嗌後衛煩啲，定係後衛亂嗌keeper煩啲</blockquote><br />\n一定係後衛亂嗌keeper煩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龍門企最後正常睇得清楚好多,屌下啲位<br />\n啲後衛係事但咁鳩嗌keeper"},{"pid":"edeebba7714a7c6ed9391ef8ca1af7566d793d27","tid":462582,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>龍門嗌後衛煩啲，定係後衛亂嗌keeper煩啲</blockquote><br />\n一定係後衛亂嗌keeper煩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龍門企最後正常睇得清楚好多,屌下啲位<br />\n啲後衛係事但咁鳩嗌keeper</blockquote><br />\n波都未撚傳叫定keeper"},{"pid":"f33c31b60154f840ee14e6fac6eaeb856511c40a","tid":462582,"uid":103346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:40:59.000Z","msg":"玩開玩具籃球<br />\n都會會踢波<br />\n<br />\n好自然會去守龍<br />\n反應會好好多，始終可以用手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057c73836b1859b408175794d8673dfcbeabfc55","tid":462582,"uid":42072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:43:38.000Z","msg":"元堂守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b068b55334ea84fd4ad6911c03fa68f280d668d7","tid":462582,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"細個睇足球小將就鍾意守<br />\n大個真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564dfe5a7dc8a027ebacd750650b3f06c47f79dd","tid":462582,"uid":60177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打槍game都鍾意醫療兵救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a684cf15f1f6eefc9d207e7ca0c90d703a902109","tid":462582,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"當你見到對面條撚樣腳瓜粗到起撚哂展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係你5個身位內爆撚哂青筋起腳怒射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰秒真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e8a7cefaf165aa3799cf5e7816b7609435adaf","tid":462582,"uid":71694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打槍game都鍾意醫療兵救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乸型廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb38e09cdb9d328c099a323645a5ba8a527c20ec","tid":462582,"uid":83927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:05:10.000Z","msg":"鐘意比人省  有鋪m 癮"},{"pid":"ec701891c6115eb860993b8808e1c9b997d97554","tid":462582,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然打龍會承受好大壓力<br />\n或者失波會唔開心<br />\n但如果因為你撲到球波而令你隊波贏既話<br />\n打龍會好滿足囉</blockquote><br />\n真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人哋入極都入唔到嗰下feel真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁做後衛都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307bfd52c3450e3babeffa47ee112d7169ff4df5","tid":462582,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:07:52.000Z","msg":"我次次轉龍接完人地果球會碌返個波比佢再射玩弄佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62981672f2cf665b3f72f919d23a25edf081cb3","tid":462582,"uid":5172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"試過學界就係守到全場唯一一球單刀，拎埋冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完場流埋馬尿"},{"pid":"80f6c5c6312963ce08b2558ed7268640dfb7b8b4","tid":462582,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"以前踢波好鐘意打龍，唔會驚波，最正係踢街場果陣其他隊會r你去佢果隊幫手守龍，咁又可以踢多場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3190b216e0de6b29429397c575eedb0bfcae9e","tid":462582,"uid":902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:22:59.000Z","msg":"我堅鐘意<br />\n睇舒米高大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f242de4d1ca46964f5702d4cd82be924d647cc","tid":462582,"uid":54472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"打過龍先知防守跟人嘅重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有次連續幾球都係比人單刀真係打到灰"},{"pid":"28c00788cc1ae6cfc5650556545194072dd57367","tid":462582,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"如果對弱隊 人地成場都冇攻門<br />\n真係得個企字<br />\n唔悶咩"},{"pid":"da83e3e503afcb77e5a7d368067d07e5e6478f28","tid":462582,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"梗係中場<br />\n<br />\n球隊的大腦"},{"pid":"07013171bcabc2c47b91127886c538bd5cecd94f","tid":462582,"uid":115181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗跑，幾好丫</blockquote><br />\n傻啦 練波攰到傻"},{"pid":"b109d1963f002294a13df6d2ae4591c602b3d11b","tid":462582,"uid":136901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"其實做龍門飛撲嘅時候真係好爽<br />\n龍門嘅訓練比場區球員更加辛苦<br />\n如果真係接受過訓練嘅<br />\n先會明白做龍門係一種享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5a4e571d40bc8f8bbe347385452cf1425a2b97","tid":462582,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打槍game都鍾意醫療兵救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乸型廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n然後你救番果個人<br />\n又衝出去殺晒人地得番一半血果班人"},{"pid":"505376a9d5f0fdf07f22d7b5af2eecb152e91df6","tid":462582,"uid":85606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"自從扭呀出現 我識得既龍都開始扭呀扭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b77ea5f1d1e6ce86bcb8ab67813e3e2a3f756ad","tid":462582,"uid":28,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"男人老狗享受比人射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46287d16b94067aceed3368a61d6bd6c2ef72694","tid":462582,"uid":39072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"龍門都可以好型喎，有時望著D必入嘅波一野比keeper 撲走左真係心心眼左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2a1e34aeb4f805ee1b234e6c173bbd4359485e","tid":462582,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T13